--- !u!114 &658036485999083271
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 8443086366334651686}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8b94c1195cc9272d99a82df3df77782b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ArtifactForm: 0
  Names:
  - Bloomy
  - Romeo
  Lines:
  - I want a divorce! There's no fire in our relationship, Romeo!
  - We've discussed this so many times, darli-
  - DON'T YOU DARE CALL ME DARLING!
  - I'm sorry, Bloomy...
  - HERE IT IS AGAIN! He's unbearably sweet! He can't even yell at me properly!
  - Can't we really be together without fighting? I don't like conflict...
  - NO, WE CANNOT! Get a divorce now! Not only did I get this whiner, but I also
    have that clingy Rosa and her Hypnus. I'm sick of them already.
  - And I was hoping we could be as happy as they are... After all, we're their artifac-
  - MAYBE YOU CAN'T LIVE A DAY WITHOUT YOUR HYPNUS, SO NICE HE POLISHES YOU, BUT
    THIS SOFT ROSE IS IMPOSSIBLE TO TOLERATE.
  - Please, do as she says... I'm really scared...
  - Exactly! For once you said something to the point.
